# UI/UX Design Intelligence

- Use curated, harmonious color palettes (not generic red/blue/green)
- Modern typography (Inter, Roboto, Outfit) — never browser defaults
- Smooth gradients, micro-animations, glassmorphism
- Hover effects and interactive elements for engagement
- Premium feel — not minimum viable product
- Dark mode support
- Responsive layouts
- Verify visually before declaring done
